text: Chinatown in London is in Soho area in the West End. It has Chinese-run businesses. These include restaurants, bakeries, supermarkets and souvenir shops.Rob Humphreys; et al, London (London: Rough Guides, 2003), p. 116 == Related pages == *British Chinese == References == == Other websites == *Chinatown website Category:City of Westminster
